<h1 class="textfont">About<img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/About.png" alt="" /></h1>

<p>
    Mythical Canines is a RPG (Role Playing Game) about K9's with special classes who attack and defend from the Cattens who are trying to invade their land.
    You (the player) have lost all of your memory and have no idea how you got here and why you're sleeping near a big glowing elder tree. <br />
    Your character encounters a animal like creature that looks like a dog but you are unsure from the mysterious cloak it wears.<br />
    The mysterious character steps towards you and this is where your journey will begin.
</p>

<div class="text-center">
    <img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/MK9Awaken.png" alt="" />
</div>

<p>
    You the player get a chance to claim and choose one of the four classes available to you.<br />
    Knight, Thief, Mage and Medic.<br />
    The mysterious character would like to give you this offer as a welcoming gift to this world in exchange for helping K9's and stopping Cattens.<br />
    You'll encounter a lot of interesting characters and Cattens along the way.<br />
    For example, one of the Catten's you'll meet is Livid.<br />
</p>

